OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780646725
OL,3,CTeenager appears in court charged over
OL,4,C'bomb hoax' at Birmingham Peter Kay
OL,5,Cshow
OL,7,FA 19-year-old has appeared in court
OL,8,Fcharged over an alleged bomb hoax
OL,9,Fwhich forced a Peter Kay comedy show
OL,10,Fto be evacuated.
OL,12,FOmar Majed appeared at Birmingham
OL,13,FCrown Court via video-link from HMP
OL,14,FBrinsford on Tuesday, June 2. He was
OL,15,Fnot asked to give a plea during the
OL,16,Fhearing due to the need for
OL,17,Fpsychiatric reports.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
