CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780646725
OL,3,CTeenager appears in court charged over
OL,4,C'bomb hoax' at Birmingham Peter Kay
OL,5,Cshow
OL,7,FA further case management hearing for
OL,8,FMajed, of Saltley, Birmingham, who was
OL,9,Fcharged with communicating false
OL,10,Finformation to police contrary to the
OL,11,FCriminal Law Act, was set for July 27.
OL,13,FA provisional date for a trial,
OL,14,Flasting two weeks, was scheduled for
OL,15,FNovember 3.
OL,17,FPeter Kay was ushered off stage during
OL,18,Fhis show at the Utilita Arena in
OL,19,FBirmingham on May 1 and the show was
OL,20,Fcancelled after the evacuation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
