PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780646725
OL,3,CTeenager appears in court charged over
OL,4,C'bomb hoax' at Birmingham Peter Kay
OL,5,Cshow
OL,7,FWest Midlands Police later said
OL,8,F"nothing suspicious was found" during
OL,9,Fsearches.
OL,11,FIn an update on May 2, the force said:
OL,12,F"An evacuation of the arena was
OL,13,Fordered yesterday evening after a
OL,14,Freport of a suspicious bag being left
OL,15,Fin the area.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@^O]tD@AOU
