OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780646725
OL,3,CTeenager appears in court charged over
OL,4,C'bomb hoax' at Birmingham Peter Kay
OL,5,Cshow
OL,7,F"Following searches, nothing
OL,8,Fsuspicious was found and we are
OL,9,Fgrateful to everyone for their co-
OL,10,Foperation and understanding. As
OL,11,Falways, our priority is the safety of
OL,12,Fthe public."
OL,14,FThe show was part of Kay's Better Late
OL,15,FThan Never national tour, which will
OL,16,Fsee all proceeds donated to 12 cancer
OL,17,Fcharities.
